<s> John E. Hayes Jr. was elected chairman , president and chief executive officer , succeeding David S. Black , who retired . </s>
<s> Mr. Hayes , 52 years old , left Southwestern Bell Telephone Co. in January , where he had been chairman , president and chief executive , to join Triad Capital Partners , a St. Louis company with interests in solid waste and recycling , telecommunications and international venture capital . </s>
<s> He has resigned his posts at Triad to take the Kansas Power positions . </s>
<s> Kansas Power said Mr. Black , 61 , chose early retirement . </s>
